          <briefdescription>
<para>name &quot;renderedScaleFactor&quot;, type <ref refid="structDali_1_1Vector2" kindref="compound">Vector2</ref> or FLOAT </para>
          </briefdescription>
          <detaileddescription>
<para>The scale factor between source scene and rendered target. For example, if we render 200x200 scene into 50x400 FBO, rendered scale factor is <ref refid="structDali_1_1Vector2" kindref="compound">Vector2</ref>(0.5f, 2.0f). If property set as float type, value become assigned componentwise. @SINCE_2_4.36 </para>
